Subject: [PATCH 1463/5242] MLK-13729-1 ARM: imx: add the reg into the rpmsg
 node

commit  5ef6392dc4b14a74fcd885a570c520ed7bb85e20 from
https://source.codeaurora.org/external/imx/linux-imx.git

In order to remove the hard-coded vring buffer in
the driver, input the vring buffer by device tree
node.

Signed-off-by: Richard Zhu <hongxing.zhu@nxp.com>
Signed-off-by: Meng Li <Meng.Li@windriver.com>
